### Search with YAML format (returns pure YAML strings)
POST http://localhost:8090/api/spec/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "How to get inventory",
  "topK": 2,
  "responseFormat": "yaml"
}

### Search with Meta format (returns SearchResult objects)
POST http://localhost:8090/api/spec/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "How to get inventory",
  "topK": 2,
  "responseFormat": "meta"
}

### Search without responseFormat (defaults to meta)
POST http://localhost:8090/api/spec/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "How to get pets by status",
  "topK": 1
}

### Search for component with YAML format
POST http://localhost:8090/api/spec/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Pet schema",
  "topK": 1,
  "responseFormat": "yaml"
}
